            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358215",
        "quote": "Just as a mother finds pleasure in taking her little child on her lap, there to feed and caress him, in like manner our loving God shows His fondness for His beloved souls who have given themselves entirely to Him and have placed all their hope in His goodness.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358215"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Mom",
                "url": "/topics/mom"
            },
            {
                "name": "Placed",
                "url": "/topics/placed"
            },
            {
                "name": "Manner",
                "url": "/topics/manner"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358210",
        "quote": "God is displeased at the diffidence of souls who love Him sincerely and whom He Himself loves.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358210"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Himself",
                "url": "/topics/himself"
            },
            {
                "name": "Sincerely",
                "url": "/topics/sincerely"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358216",
        "quote": "Not only is there no need of an intermediary through whom He would want you to speak to Him, but He finds His delight in having you treat with Him personally and in all confidence.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358216"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Treat",
                "url": "/topics/treat"
            },
            {
                "name": "Through",
                "url": "/topics/through"
            },
            {
                "name": "Having",
                "url": "/topics/having"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358202",
        "quote": "Acquire the habit of speaking to God as if you were alone with Him, familiarly and with confidence and love, as to the dearest and most loving of friends.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358202"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Confidence",
                "url": "/topics/confidence"
            },
            {
                "name": "Dearest",
                "url": "/topics/dearest"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358219",
        "quote": "Since His delights are to be with you, let yours be found in Him.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358219"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "God",
                "url": "/topics/god"
