                "url": "/topics/plans"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358227",
        "quote": "Yet you should practice the greatest possible love and confidence in treating with Him.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358227"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Confidence",
                "url": "/topics/confidence"
            },
            {
                "name": "Practice",
                "url": "/topics/practice"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358204",
        "quote": "Ask those who love Him with a sincere love, and they will tell you that they find no greater or prompter relief amid the troubles of their life than in loving conversation with their Divine Friend.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358204"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Faith",
                "url": "/topics/faith"
            },
            {
                "name": "Will",
                "url": "/topics/will"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358205",
        "quote": "Assuredly, Loving Souls, you should go to God with all humility and respect, humbling yourselves in His presence, especially when you remember your past ingratitude and sins.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358205"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Respect",
                "url": "/topics/respect"
            },
            {
                "name": "Past",
                "url": "/topics/past"
            },
            {
                "name": "Humility",
                "url": "/topics/humility"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358208",
        "quote": "But You never reject a repentant and humble heart.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358208"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Humble",
                "url": "/topics/humble"
            },
            {
                "name": "Never",
                "url": "/topics/never"
            },
            {
                "name": "Reject",
                "url": "/topics/reject"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358211",
        "quote": "If you wish to strengthen your confidence in God still more, often recall the loving way in which He has acted toward you, and how mercifully He has tried to bring you out of your sinful life, to break your attachment to the things of earth and draw you to His love.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358211"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Bring",
                "url": "/topics/bring"
            },
            {
                "name": "Your",
                "url": "/topics/your"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358213",
        "quote": "It is a great mistake, as we have already remarked, to be afraid of Him and to act in His presence like a timid and craven slave trembling with fright before his master.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358213"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Mistake",
                "url": "/topics/mistake"
            },
            {
                "name": "Like",
                "url": "/topics/like"
            },
            {
                "name": "Before",
                "url": "/topics/before"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358214",
        "quote": "Job was astonished at seeing Almighty God so intent on doing good to us that He seems to have nothing more at heart than to love us and to induce us to love Him in return.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358214"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Almighty God",
                "url": "/topics/almighty_god"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358217",
        "quote": "Nothing else is required than to act toward God, in the midst of your occupations, as you do, even when busy, toward those who love you and whom you love.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358217"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
