                "url": "/topics/your"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358223",
        "quote": "True, He is infinite Majesty, but He is also infinite Goodness and infinite Love. There can be no greater Lord than God; neither can there be a more ardent lover than He.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358223"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Infinite",
                "url": "/topics/infinite"
            },
            {
                "name": "Ardent",
                "url": "/topics/ardent"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358225",
        "quote": "Who is there that ever receives a gift and tries to make bargains about it? Let us, then, return thanks for what He has bestowed on us. Who can tell whether, if we had had a larger share of ability or stronger health, we should not have possessed them to our destruction.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Alphonsus Liguori",
            "url": "/quotes/alphonsus_liguori_358225"
        },
